# During `tauri dev` the opencode sidecar inherits src-tauri/ as its working
# directory and writes its runtime config/auth/state there. Without this, every
# config change (selecting a model, saving a provider key) makes opencode write
# a file here, which the dev watcher treats as a source change and rebuilds —
# restarting the app mid-action. Ignore opencode's runtime artifacts.
config.json
opencode.json
opencode.jsonc
auth.json
.opencode/
storage/
*.log
